  "steps": [
    {
      "title": "Cut wood.",
      "body": "Using a miter saw, cut the wood down to size. There are three pieces total for each shelf. Our shelves were designed with a 1x3 piece on the back, 1x3 piece on the bottom and 1x2 on the front side.\nOur shelves are 4 feet wide, which fits well in the hallway space that they are going in.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/fe75f178ef6e624c.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Drill pocket holes.",
      "body": "On the bottom piece of wood (one of the 1x3 pieces) drill 5 pocket holes with a Kreg Jig. We spaced them out 1\" from the edges and then 1 foot spacing between each pocket hole.\nThe pocket hole placement is detailed in the woodworking plans, which can be found in the Extras tab.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/a3bde082cc032b83.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Attach front.",
      "body": "Using 1 1/4\" pocket hole screws, attach the front piece to the bottom."
    },
    {
      "title": "Attach back.",
      "body": "Using wood glue and 2\" finish nails approximately every 5 inches or so, attach the back piece.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/785d9ae0abc123f0.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Fill pocket holes.",
      "body": "Using pocket hole plugs and wood glue, fill pocket holes for a more finished look.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/ce7fd4807bdd65b6.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Sand.",
      "body": "Sand the entire shelf well with an orbital sander and 80 grit sandpaper for shaping and then with 150 grit for finishing.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/46883a8c4f6fc7c7.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Stain.",
      "body": "With your stain of choice, apply stain on the entire shelf. Alternatively, you could also paint the picture ledge shelves!\nWe used Dark Walnut stain by Miniwax.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/ba7b8fce7c6551e6.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Seal.",
      "body": "Once stain has set in, apply polyurethane over the entire shelf."
    }
  ],
